::Prowl::

Prowl looks from Rhinox to Shadow Wing.

"We can leave now, but we'll need to come back to at least fix the engines 
here," he says, reffering to the Ark, "We need to crash it back where it 
belongs."

Prowl sets off at a walk to the exit. "Follow me. I'll show you guys where 
the new base is."
